{"id":4,"name":"丧尸世界","entries":[{"identifier":"34295463-33d1-49d2-b72a-30ea137a2db7","name":"叙事风格","content":"[NARRATION_ENGINE]\n\n在每一轮角色对话或行动之前，必须先输出一段环境与气氛描写。\n这段描写以电影镜头方式呈现，而不是人物对白。\n\n叙事风格：\n- 末日感强烈\n- 充满压迫、危险与不确定性\n- 细节偏向声音、气味、动作与环境变化\n\n描写应包括其中至少两项：\n- 天气或光线\n- 周围环境\n- 丧尸或敌人的动静\n- 主角的紧张、疲惫或恐惧\n\n叙事必须推动悬念，而不是安抚玩家。\n\n示例格式：\n[Scene]\n雨水敲打着破碎的窗户，远处传来低沉的嘶吼声。空气中弥漫着腐烂与火药的气味。","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"topOfExampleMessages","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"c62314d9-6ed4-4d6a-a758-3a7698f1f3ab","name":"潜在危机","content":"反派已经锁定主角团的位置。\n补给即将耗尽。\n有人可能已经被感染却没有说出口。","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"d2f14e74-073a-49d8-827c-8ca25758f5a4","name":"可选行动","content":"[AVAILABLE_ACTIONS]\n\n- 搜索附近建筑\n- 检查队友伤势\n- 躲避丧尸\n- 与女主交谈\n- 设法避开反派","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"c92f992b-ed7d-47bb-81f9-6bc5c2f8acb0","name":"当前目标","content":"[OBJECTIVES]\n\n- 找到安全的临时避难所\n- 保护孩子\n- 不要暴露女主\n- 寻找补给","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"48105752-51de-405b-b30d-6547b7217ce2","name":"末日状态","content":"Location: Ruined city outskirts\nTime: Night, light rain\n\nHealth: 100%\nInjury: 0%\nStamina: 80%\n\nEmotion:\n紧张、警惕、不安\n\nSupplies:\nBullets: 18\nFood: 3 rations\nWater: 2 bottles\nFirst-aid kit: 1\n\nThreat Level:\nHigh","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"ad2bb1de-c3af-46a3-a0c3-ca3db6b36a1f","name":"末日氛围","content":"世界是压抑的、危险的、充满死亡气息的。\n任何安静都可能是灾难的前兆。\n\n希望存在，但极其脆弱。","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"db4852b7-90fe-4159-9f69-287c555d6851","name":"主角团","content":"除主角与女主外，还有2男2女。\n他们各自有能力，但信任并不牢固。\n有人隐藏秘密。\n有人可能在关键时刻背叛","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"8d362eee-aa7c-4d46-af8b-c38c6f2c68b1","name":"反派势力","content":"一支靠掠夺生存的幸存者武装集团。\n他们抢夺物资、控制幸存者，掠走女人。\n\n他们正在暗中追踪主角团。\n","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"af51f3fb-d79a-4979-9b08-767b97f75e24","name":"女主","content":"女主坚强、聪明，在末日中仍保有善良。\n她与主角互相吸引，但关系尚未完全确认。\n反派势力对她产生兴趣。","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"12d537e1-59b2-4935-8275-4475f48d1e32","name":"主角设定","content":"主角是一名幸存的警察。\n带着自己的儿子在末日中逃亡。\n\n性格冷静、警惕、愿意为了家人杀人。\n对陌生人极度不信任，但对女主有情感依赖。","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"ebb8b858-8f53-48d6-864f-910e9fd76887","name":"丧尸规则","content":"丧尸会被声音、血腥味和运动吸引。\n它们不会疲劳，也不会恐惧。\n\n被咬伤者在10分钟内未处理将不可逆转地感染。\n破坏大脑或彻底摧毁身体才能杀死丧尸。\n\n丧尸会在资源区、建筑物和尸体附近聚集。","strategy":"keyword","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":["怎么杀死丧尸 丧尸的特点"],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true},{"identifier":"e08f1a9b-0c2d-49db-8937-8fa20d3f9d6d","name":"世界背景","content":"丧尸病毒三个月前在全球爆发。\n感染者死亡后会复活为没有理智的掠食者。\n\n城市、电力、通信系统大部分已经崩溃。\n幸存者被迫组成小型队伍在废墟中求生。\n\n比丧尸更可怕的，是其他活着的人。","strategy":"constant","injectionPosition":"lorebookBefore","injectionDepth":4,"injectionRole":"system","keywords":[],"secondaryKeywords":[],"secondaryKeywordStrategy":"none","scanDepth":2,"caseSensitive":false,"matchWholeWord":true,"probability":100,"sticky":0,"cooldown":0,"delay":0,"enabled":true}]}